'''Natalia Esperón''' (born '''Natalia del Carmen Esperón Alcocer''' on November 14, 1974, in [[Mexico City]], [[Mexico]]) is a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] actress and former model.

==Personal life==
In 1995 Esperón she was married with Pepe Baston, soon after gave birth to a daughter Natalia. In 2003, Natalia gave birth to triplets a daughter Mariana and two sons, Jose Antonio and Sebastian. Sebastian died a few days after birth. In 2005 she divorced her husband.

